Build instructions:
ghc --make lab1.hs
./lab1 text1.txt text2.txt
or
./lab1
(to read from stdin, use Ctrl+D as delimeter)

Note:
I strip off punctuation at the beginning and end of a word, but let the ones in the middle stay.
Examples:
  don't = don't
  text!! = text
  "string" = string
